message.body: Hi baby. How was your day? Mine just got loopy. I just found out the performance is back on but lost Zac & Mark's numbers when I switched phones today.
Let's give up and snuggle.
Sounds loopy indeed, glad the performance is a go though! Snuggle u supreme.
It's not actually because I can't get in touch with them now and don't know where they are. It's supposed to start in a few minutes. I'm ready for the beach.
Shit! Can u get their #s somehow? Btw, my day is boring in comparison, worked for trever cutting foam for art, now off to design bat wingshapes
I just managed to find them in my old phone, but didn't get ahold of them.
Oof. I hope that they arrive soon! Anyway yeah, lets go to the beeeech
I,m seeing a rainbow in the sky! And I waited for you to slide down, but wtf? I,ll just wait at the bottom I guess.
Ok I'll be there quick! Lemme finish this beer with bee!
M & Z ever show up?
No. I leaned in paint and then ate a sammy and I'm hangin out with my friend Jenn
Huh, so weird they didnt show... What color paint is now all over you?
Red orange hold on imma try to take a picture of a cute kittay
￼Fluffier!
Cant get the pic! Send agin?
Aw ok, just a fluff ball
Nawp, must be your new fone spanking my geezer.
Noooooooo it's so fluffy!
The fone is fluffy, ifone?
Kittay fluffy, resonance slop
Splooge colored
Wish u cud take a picture of your own phone
Ha! Just google iPhone 4S. I researched solar chargers!
Was your bros oldie? Solar is so nice. I,m resaerching LED bat eyes. You,d make em glow pink.
No, I got it free from Verizon joining the family plan
But I need to solve this boyfriend pictures thing. I need to visually snug you with kitten fur!
I think I emailed them to you
Oh shit, prolly paying centimes now...
Maybe jes come over, ya
So soon my sweet!
Thanks for keeping old skool wid me baby
I'm hangin at Jenns place with her and her ex boyfriend who still lives here. It's quite comical. Very endearing.
Holy shit that is a cute kitti
There's 2, Lucy and desi
Two kittis, one for each eyeball... sleepytime for these eyeballs... Miss you runt
Miss you too my paenie. Here's to the last balloon gig for a little while. Kittay pillows with you soon.
I'm going on a boat with Zac and Mark!
Whoa cool! You,re all so bouyantt!
Mark brought us to a gay piano bar in a manhattan basement. They were playing over the rainbow when we walked in. I'm tellin yer mom.
Goodnight fuzz lump. So sleepy. I'm bottling the fun for u.
Aw, gunite baby! Just got home, drove to my parents for more shroooms and ramps. Missin u biggies!
I hope yr Gavin fun rampin it up. Kiss a tree for me, and an oozy kittay, and some angelic parents!
Havin fun. Paenutbutterfingers.
All deinstalled peanut. I hope your rampin was fruitful, and the fam is indulgent. Imma try to snag a cab on the walk home. Will you carry me?
Baby! Finally found my charger! We,re hedded back to mpls via lake city. We found 38 lbs of Morels! Then got insanely drunk around a fire! How was NY su/mon? Can we earsnug tonight?
You're rich with debauchery! Forest gold! Yes pleeze. I'm upstate again, this time with signal.
Oookay, so nice. Feels like i,ve been gone/unplugged for so long...
Yes I'm missing you and wanting to join you in the woods.
K, i,ll ring in a couple hrs when we arrive in mpls. Miss u baby sweets!
